sql_query.sql: SELECT "atk_jadwal"."id", "atk_jadwal"."tahun", "atk_jadwal"."pengajuan_mulai", "atk_jadwal"."pengajuan_selesai", "atk_jadwal"."status", "atk_jadwal"."keterangan", "atk_jadwal"."updated", "atk_jadwal"."created" FROM "atk_jadwal" WHERE "atk_jadwal"."tahun" = 2023 ORDER BY "atk_jadwal"."updated" DESC, "atk_jadwal"."created" DESC LIMIT 1
